  <brief_title>Predictor for an Additional Benefit of Inhaled Corticosteroid in Patients Treated With Tiotropium for COPD</brief_title>
  <official_title>Predictor for an Additional Benefit of Inhaled Corticosteroid in Patients Treated With Tiotropium for Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD)</official_title>
