      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  FEV1/FVC &lt; 70%

          -  FEV1 % predicted &gt; 60%

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Other major disease

          -  Asthma

          -  Currently taking inhaled corticosteroids

          -  oral corticosteroids in the last 3 month

